{"tid":1182820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李家超：修例不寫額外人權保障為保靈活性","createTime":"2019-06-02T12:46:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-02T14:32:24.000Z","uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7f9761c4de604e00bba9fb757700af91d3fd8243","tid":1182820,"uid":7828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T12:46:53.000Z","msg":"保安局局長李家超指，逃犯條例中沒寫入額外人權保障是為了保持靈活性，又指申請移交的一方必須要遵循協議，落實當中的人權保障。<br />\n<br />\n律政司司長鄭若驊、保安局局長李家超一起出席電台節目，解說逃犯條例修訂。<br />\n<br />\n李家超表示，條例通過後不只是處理移交內地的個案，亦有其他司法管轄區，因此沒有把額外人權要求寫入法例是保留靈活性。<br />\n<br />\n外界很多關注都是內地司法制度不可信，李家超認為，涉及移交的罪類在內地都是公開審訊。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊指，知道有立法會議員就條例提出修正案，這些都交由立法會處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=350200\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D350200&d=nzMqhIG%2BVuPatXbgV3aJI%2BxpY9ERoCMedVnvBBvIoB8%3D&h=33e0855c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D350200&h=99eea885\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=350200</a>"},{"pid":"3a5e844755199268d9d2050af654b8a2c3bb146e","tid":1182820,"uid":7828,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T12:48:04.000Z","msg":"保持靈活性，方便隨時搬龍門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae26e7039076d8b8e138b8c3f9b306db35fd3e73","tid":1182820,"uid":14816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T12:51:30.000Z","msg":"公開審訊，遵循協議，真係全部都係廢話喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"453aefb30ff1761e6d66ced549fc0ec46731977a","tid":1182820,"uid":103981,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-02T12:53:08.000Z","msg":"要靈活咪每次都一次性安排囉 <br />\n大家傾好先交<br />\n仲修咩例？"},{"pid":"c425c94a26cc275f1b5251d935e1c1cf9699bae9","tid":1182820,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3